title: Naked
overview: Hotelier Rishabh Mehta is found murdered. An honest cop, Suraj Kadam, begins investigating the case and meets Natasha Kamra, the prime suspect, who is also a porn star by profession. Will Suraj be able to find the real killer? Is Natasha really guilty or is she just an easy target?  Sometimes, the truth is nothing but just a naked illusion.
